  "title": "Assistant Accountant / Accountant (Food Manufacturing Co./Woodland Area)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Manage comprehensive accounting functions to deliver accurate financial reporting and support audit processes, contributing to organizational financial integrity and compliance.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage the full set of accounts to ensure accurate and timely financial records</li><li>Prepare management accounts and audit schedules to support internal and external audit processes</li><li>Review subsidiary accounts and analyze variances to identify discrepancies and inform financial decision-making</li><li>Liaise with external auditors to coordinate audit activities and resolve audit queries effectively</li><li>Execute additional accounting tasks as required to support business operations and financial controls</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Accountancy or its equivalent</li><li>Minimum 5 years of experience independently handling full set of accounts</li><li>Experience in a food manufacturing company</li></ul><p><br />5 days work week<br />Woodland Area<br />Food Manufacturing Co. <br /><br />Interested Applicants, kindly email your detailed resume to <a href=\"mailto:hr@tempserv.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">hr@tempserv.com.sg</a></p><p><strong>Tempserv Pte Ltd</strong></p><p>License No: 06C3745</p><p><strong>Attention: Audris Teo / EA Personnel No: R1102063</strong></p>",
